Given a pair of tree traversal, return true if a unique binary tree can be constructed otherwise false. 
Each traversal is represented with integer: 1 -> Preorder , 2 -> Inorder , 3 -> Postorder.


code::

class Solution{	
	public:	
		bool uniqueBinaryTree(int a, int b){
		    if(a == 2 || b == 2) return true;
		    return false;
		}
};


complexity analysis::

TC: O(1)
SC: O(1)
